<font color="#FF0000">WHEN YOUR IN A RUT</font><br>
<tt>Fri Sep 19 19:10:31 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
MTF,<br><br>
You must be getting old.  When I was in your country last week the local boys said that rut was in two weeks early.  Your late, better rush out and mark your territory and knock that fuzz off you antlers.<br><br>
Had a young one fall in love with my old Chevy Truck.  Bumper crop the corn is tall.  I to like the bow and back powder.  I just have a hell of a time getting the arrows down the barrel.<br><br>
SW
